ince its inception, breaking has evolved into a competitive art form.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its inception\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitive art form\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An MC narrates the movements, while a DJ mixes songs to create a dynamic atmosphere.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An MC narrates\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"the movements\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"a DJ\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"songs\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"a dynamic atmosphere\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics will feature two events: one for men, called B-boys, and one for women, called B-girls.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"two events\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"B-boys\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"B-girls\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In these events, athletes will face off in dance battles.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these events\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"dance battles\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes earn points forcreativity, personality, technique, variety, performativity and musicality.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"points forcreativity\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"personality\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"technique\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"variety\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"performativity\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"musicality\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Success in this sport requires combiningdance moves from three basic categories: top rock, down rock and freeze.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Success\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"combiningdance moves\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"three basic categories\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"top rock\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"rock\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"freeze\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Top rockmoves are performed while standing up, focusing on fancy footwork and hand movements.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Top rockmoves\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"fancy footwork\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"hand movements\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These movements are reminiscent of hip-hop dancing.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These movements\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop dancing\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Top rock moves rely on having lots of friction between an athlete's shoes and the floor.Friction is the forcethat resists when you slide something across a surface.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Top rock moves\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2022}, {\"ngram\": \"friction\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete's shoes\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"Friction\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"forcethat\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"a surface\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This friction allows the athlete to take very quick steps and to stop abruptly.\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This friction\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"very quick steps\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dancersmust intuitively understand inertia, or the fact that their bodies will continue in the direction they are moving unless they are acted upon by an external force.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The dancersmust\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"inertia\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"their bodies\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"the direction\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"an external force\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To stop abruptly, athletes need to engage their muscles, getting their shoes to grip the ground to stop themselves from continuing forward.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"their muscles\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"their shoes\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Down rock moves are performed while on the floor.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rock moves\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes may spin in circles with their head, back, elbows or shoulders touching the ground and their feet in the air.B-boysandB-girlsrely heavily on an internal knowledge of physics to complete these moves.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"circles\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"their head\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"elbows\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"shoulders\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"their feet\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"B\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"an internal knowledge\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"physics\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"these moves\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Consider the physics of a backspin.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the physics\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"a backspin\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A backspin occurs when the athlete ison their back with their feet liftedin the air, rotating around a specific area of their back.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A backspin\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"their back\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2894}, {\"ngram\": \"their feet\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2927}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific area\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"their back\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sitting on the floor, the athlete's left foot stays in contact with the floor while they spread their right leg wide,gathering linear momentumas they sweep their right leg toward their left foot in a wide arc.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's left foot\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"their right leg\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3088}, {\"ngram\": \"linear momentumas\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"their right leg\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"their left foot\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"a wide arc\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, they release their left leg from contact with the ground and roll onto their back.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their left leg\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3220}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"their back\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that only their back is in contact with the ground, the linear momentum from their leg turns intoangular momentum, which rotates the athlete around an axis that extends upward from their back's contact point with the ground.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only their back\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3301}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"the linear momentum\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"their leg\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3367}, {\"ngram\": \"intoangular momentum\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3421}, {\"ngram\": \"an axis\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"their back's contact point\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3488}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This move turns magical when they bring their legs and arms inward, toward the axis of rotation.\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This move\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"their legs\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"arms\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"the axis\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"rotation\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This principal is calledconservation of angular momentum.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This principal\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3617}, {\"ngram\": \"calledconservation\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"angular momentum\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When an athlete brings their mass in more closely to the axis of rotation, the athlete's rotations speed up.\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3677}, {\"ngram\": \"their mass\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3695}, {\"ngram\": \"the axis\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3723}, {\"ngram\": \"rotation\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3735}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's rotations\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Extending their legs and arms once again and moving their mass away from theaxis of rotationwill cause the competitor to slow their rotation speed down.\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 3923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their legs\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3791}, {\"ngram\": \"arms\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"their mass\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3833}, {\"ngram\": \"theaxis\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"rotationwill\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3867}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitor\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3888}, {\"ngram\": \"their rotation speed\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once they slow down, they can transition to another move.\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another move\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freeze occurs whenathletes come to a stop in a funky pose, often occurring in time to the music and in an upside-down position.\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 4110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Freeze\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3989}, {\"ngram\": \"whenathletes\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"a stop\", \"from\": 4018, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"a funky pose\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4040}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4061, \"to\": 4065}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4078}, {\"ngram\": \"an upside-down position\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To freeze effectively, the athlete must have full control over their center of mass, placing it right above the point of their body that is in contact with the floor.\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4145}, {\"ngram\": \"full control\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4168}, {\"ngram\": \"their center\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4186}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4194}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4228}, {\"ngram\": \"their body\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4242}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4261}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The center of mass is the average position of all the parts of an athlete, weighted according to their masses.\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The center\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4288}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4296}, {\"ngram\": \"the average position\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"all the parts\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4341, \"to\": 4351}, {\"ngram\": \"their masses\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"balance point\\\" where the entire mass of the athlete seems to be concentrated is the center of mass.\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The \\\"balance point\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire mass\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4430}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4445}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 4474, \"to\": 4484}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 4488, \"to\": 4492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes are most stable when their center of mass is as close to the ground as possible.\", \"from\": 4495, \"to\": 4584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 4495, \"to\": 4503}, {\"ngram\": \"their center\", \"from\": 4525, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will see many competitors freeze witharms bentin an effort to lower their center of mass.\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many competitors\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4614}, {\"ngram\": \"witharms\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4630}, {\"ngram\": \"an effort\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4647}, {\"ngram\": \"their center\", \"from\": 4657, \"to\": 4669}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This lowered center of mass reduces their distance from the floor and minimizes the tendency of their body to rock to one side or the other due to torque.\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This lowered center\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4698}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4706}, {\"ngram\": \"their distance\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4729}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4744}, {\"ngram\": \"the tendency\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4771}, {\"ngram\": \"their body\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4785}, {\"ngram\": \"rock\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4793}, {\"ngram\": \"one side\", \"from\": 4797, \"to\": 4805}, {\"ngram\": \"torque\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Torque is a twisting force, like the force used to turn a wrench.\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4900, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Torque\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"a twisting force\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4861}, {\"ngram\": \"the force\", \"from\": 4868, \"to\": 4877}, {\"ngram\": \"a wrench\", \"from\": 4891, \"to\": 4899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The torque depends on two things: the amount of force you apply, and how far from the pivot point you apply the force.\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 5019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The torque\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4911}, {\"ngram\": \"two things\", \"from\": 4923, \"to\": 4933}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4945}, {\"ngram\": \"force\", \"from\": 4949, \"to\": 4954}, {\"ngram\": \"the pivot\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 4992}, {\"ngram\": \"the force\", \"from\": 5009, \"to\": 5018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With an athlete's center of mass closer to the ground, the athlete decreases the distance between the pivot point - the ground - and where the force of gravity is applied - the athlete's center of mass.\", \"from\": 5020, \"to\": 5222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete's center\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5044}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5052}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 5063, \"to\": 5073}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 5075, \"to\": 5086}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 5097, \"to\": 5109}, {\"ngram\": \"the pivot point\", \"from\": 5118, \"to\": 5133}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 5136, \"to\": 5146}, {\"ngram\": \"the force\", \"from\": 5159, \"to\": 5168}, {\"ngram\": \"gravity\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5179}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's center\", \"from\": 5193, \"to\": 5213}, {\"ngram\": \"mass\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes need great strength to halt their motion mid-movement because they have to apply a force to resist the change in inertia.\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 5224, \"to\": 5232}, {\"ngram\": \"great strength\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5252}, {\"ngram\": \"their motion\", \"from\": 5261, \"to\": 5273}, {\"ngram\": \"mid\", \"from\": 5274, \"to\": 5277}, {\"ngram\": \"movement\", \"from\": 5278, \"to\": 5286}, {\"ngram\": \"a force\", \"from\": 5314, \"to\": 5321}, {\"ngram\": \"the change\", \"from\": 5332, \"to\": 5342}, {\"ngram\": \"inertia\", \"from\": 5346, \"to\": 5353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many sports require a specific uniform.\", \"from\": 5356, \"to\": 5395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many sports\", \"from\": 5356, \"to\": 5367}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific uniform\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking does not - an athlete can wear whatever they want - but the right outfit will maximize their chance of success.\", \"from\": 5396, \"to\": 5516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 5396, \"to\": 5404}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 5416, \"to\": 5426}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 5436, \"to\": 5444}, {\"ngram\": \"the right outfit\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5477}, {\"ngram\": \"their chance\", \"from\": 5492, \"to\": 5504}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 5508, \"to\": 5515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete wants a shirt that minimizes the friction between their body and the ground during a spin.\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athlete\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5529}, {\"ngram\": \"a shirt\", \"from\": 5536, \"to\": 5543}, {\"ngram\": \"the friction\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5571}, {\"ngram\": \"their body\", \"from\": 5580, \"to\": 5590}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5605}, {\"ngram\": \"a spin\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lettering or images on the back of the shirt will add friction, which hinders an athlete's ability to perform some down rock moves.\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lettering\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5630}, {\"ngram\": \"images\", \"from\": 5634, \"to\": 5640}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5652}, {\"ngram\": \"the shirt\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5665}, {\"ngram\": \"friction\", \"from\": 5675, \"to\": 5683}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete's ability\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5719}, {\"ngram\": \"some down rock moves\", \"from\": 5731, \"to\": 5751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An athlete may choose to wear long sleeves if they plan to slide on their elbows, as bare skin in contact with the floor provides more friction.\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An athlete\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5763}, {\"ngram\": \"long sleeves\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 5795}, {\"ngram\": \"their elbows\", \"from\": 5821, \"to\": 5833}, {\"ngram\": \"bare skin\", \"from\": 5838, \"to\": 5847}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5858}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 5864, \"to\": 5873}, {\"ngram\": \"more friction\", \"from\": 5883, \"to\": 5896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes also have to think aboutthe headgear they wear.\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5907}, {\"ngram\": \"aboutthe headgear\", \"from\": 5927, \"to\": 5944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While there are many different styles of hats made specifically for breaking, the athlete gets to choose whichever fits their dancing style best.\", \"from\": 5956, \"to\": 6101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many different styles\", \"from\": 5972, \"to\": 5993}, {\"ngram\": \"hats\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6001}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 6024, \"to\": 6032}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 6034, \"to\": 6045}, {\"ngram\": \"whichever\", \"from\": 6061, \"to\": 6070}, {\"ngram\": \"their dancing style\", \"from\": 6076, \"to\": 6095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They need to make sure that their hat provides some padding for their head while minimizing the friction between their head and the floor.\", \"from\": 6102, \"to\": 6240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their hat\", \"from\": 6130, \"to\": 6139}, {\"ngram\": \"some padding\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6161}, {\"ngram\": \"their head\", \"from\": 6166, \"to\": 6176}, {\"ngram\": \"the friction\", \"from\": 6194, \"to\": 6206}, {\"ngram\": \"their head\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6225}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 6230, \"to\": 6239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The back, elbow and head are axes of rotation during down rock, so the athlete wants gear that minimizes friction at all these places.\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"elbow\", \"from\": 6252, \"to\": 6257}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 6262, \"to\": 6266}, {\"ngram\": \"axes\", \"from\": 6271, \"to\": 6275}, {\"ngram\": \"rotation\", \"from\": 6279, \"to\": 6287}, {\"ngram\": \"rock\", \"from\": 6300, \"to\": 6304}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6320}, {\"ngram\": \"gear\", \"from\": 6327, \"to\": 6331}, {\"ngram\": \"all these places\", \"from\": 6359, \"to\": 6375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they also need to make sure their shoes have grip to maximize friction while they are doing top rock footwork.\", \"from\": 6377, \"to\": 6491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their shoes\", \"from\": 6409, \"to\": 6420}, {\"ngram\": \"grip\", \"from\": 6426, \"to\": 6430}, {\"ngram\": \"friction\", \"from\": 6443, \"to\": 6451}, {\"ngram\": \"top rock footwork\", \"from\": 6473, \"to\": 6490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes also want to make sure their hands are not sweaty or slick so they can use friction from their hands to control how fast they are rotating during down rock spins.\", \"from\": 6492, \"to\": 6663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 6492, \"to\": 6500}, {\"ngram\": \"their hands\", \"from\": 6524, \"to\": 6535}, {\"ngram\": \"friction\", \"from\": 6576, \"to\": 6584}, {\"ngram\": \"their hands\", \"from\": 6590, \"to\": 6601}, {\"ngram\": \"rock spins\", \"from\": 6652, \"to\": 6662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the world of breaking - where dancers seem to defy gravity - strength and artistry work hand in hand with physics to create the moves that will captivate audiences during the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 6665, \"to\": 6857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6668, \"to\": 6677}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 6681, \"to\": 6689}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 6698, \"to\": 6705}, {\"ngram\": \"gravity - strength and artistry work hand\", \"from\": 6719, \"to\": 6760}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 6764, \"to\": 6768}, {\"ngram\": \"physics\", \"from\": 6774, \"to\": 6781}, {\"ngram\": \"the moves\", \"from\": 6792, \"to\": 6801}, {\"ngram\": \"audiences\", \"from\": 6822, \"to\": 6831}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 6839, \"to\": 6856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 6859, \"to\": 6913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 6859, \"to\": 6913}]}]}"